Use Case Template 2 :

Name : Login.

Brief description : The user have ability to login to application.

Players : Admin, User, DB.

Precondition :Enter in the CNEF's application.
                   
Basic Flow : 
1. Click on login button.
2. Login screens pops up.
3. Fill in all user informations. 
4. Press login.
5. Redirection to main page of the application.

Alternative flow : 
1. Press forgot password.
2. Redirection to confim email page.
3. The user needs to fill the email for confirm.
4. The user receive a link to reset password page.
5. Fill-in new password.
6. Submit new password. 

Exception flow : User name/Password wrong.

Post Conditions : The user has been redirected to the main page app.
